Description:
If wide range of work in statistics and numerical analysis gives you the greatest satisfaction in your daily work, our client JSC "Crefo Birojs" vacancy is for you. Join team of professionals and probably be the best

DATA SCIENCE EXPERT

If you have:
• Higher education in statistics, mathematics, computer science or a related field (may be a student);
• Good understanding of probabilities and statistical models, willingness to continue learning and developing these skills;
• Experience in fields related to data science and the ability to perform tasks using statistics;
• Interest in machine learning (ML, AI) and data modeling;
• Programming skills with Python or R, experience with SQL databases;
• Previous financial experience is not required, although an interest in business is highly desirable;
• Ability and willingness to work independently with several projects at the same time;
• Good business communication skills in presenting data to various audiences, technicians and business... teams;
• Experience with MS Azure will be an advantage.

We will entrust you:
• Creating scoring models and maintaining a full cycle according to the goals of the model and business needs;
• Help to analyze credit portfolios, predict their cash flow in various development scenarios, automate processes;
• Development and programming of complex queries for data acquisition, transformation and preparation for statistical modeling;
• Participation in the development of artificial intelligence / machine learning methods (AI / ML), providing data acquisition and statistical analysis;
• In-depth presentation of data analysis in a simple, understandable and comprehensible way, emphasizing the potential impact on different business directions (lending, sales, marketing, etc.).

Benefits for you:
• Exciting challenges and the opportunity to participate in the implementation of new projects;
• A supportive and collaborative team of professionals;
• Work in an international work environment;
• Salary 2500 - 2800 EUR gross (depending on experience and qualification);
• Social guarantees and health insurance;
• A modern and ergonomic work environment with the possibility to work remotely;
• Paid parking in Riga, Skanstes Street 50.

Find out more about employer here: https://www.crefobirojs.lv/par-mums/

